the maintenance, preservation, and architectural control of the residence lots and common area of the Association
homeowners in the County of Nye, State of Nevada, AND PURSUANT TO THE PROVISIONS OF THE
NEVADA REVISED STATUTES, claims a lien upon the real property and buildings, improvements or structures
thereon described as follows:
Lot
48
Block
16
of
CALVADA MEADOWS UNIT NO. 2
as shown on the map thereof recorded _March 4, 1980_ in the Office of the County Recorder of Nye County,
State of Nevada Under Document No. 18918, Parcel No .: 033-061-18.
Commonly known as: _ 1191 E. Langley Place, Las Vegas NV/89060
And that the whole of said real estate upon which the buildings are situated is reasonably necessary for the
convenient use and occupancy of said buildings.
That_JOE SCHOW and CAROLYN SCHOW is/are the name (s) of the owner (s) and reputed owner (s) of said
real property and improvements heroin above described.
That the prorata assessment which shall constitute a lien against the above described property amounts to $124,86
per year as provided in the DECLARATION OF COVENANTS, CONDITIONS, and RESTRICTIONS which
were recorded on
August 20, 2002 , as Document No. 540803 , and all AMENDMENTS and
ANNEXATIONS et. seq ., of Official Records of Nye County, Nevada, at Page _n/a , and which have been
supplied to and agreed to by said owner and reputed owner. That the Association had made demand for payment
of the total amount due and owing, but said sum has not been paid.
THAT THE AMOUNT OWING AND UNPAID TOTALS $1.175.00 # as of
1/03/2022
_and
INCREASES cach year at a rate of $ > 124.86 per year, plus LATE CHARGES at the rate of $ 25.00 per
month, PLUS INTEREST at the rate of _5,25% per annum, PLUS ATTORNEY FEES and the FEES of the
AGENT FOR THE MANAGEMENT BODY incurred in connection with preparation, recording, and
foreclosure of this lien. * Plus Reserve Assessment in the amount of $175.14, per year.
THE CALVADA AERO PARK ASSOCIATION,
DBA CALVADA MEADOWS AIRPORT ASSOCIATION
